	<Title>武黄高速6车追尾引发大火致3人死亡</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2008.06.13 05:10:00</ReportTime>    
	<Content><Paragraph>
    <Sentence><Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s1">本报</Participant><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">讯</Denoter></Event>（记者 周琦 谭经田 通讯员 高巡 蔺善波 实习生 王维）
    </Sentence>
<Sentence><Event eid="e2"><Time type="relTime" tid="t2">昨日凌晨</Time>，<Location lid="l2">武黄高速公路武黄向57公里处</Location>发生<Object sid="s2">6车</Object><Denoter type="emergency" did="d2">追尾</Denoter>的交通事故</Event>，<Event eid="e3">剧烈<Denoter type="action" did="d3">撞击</Denoter></Event>
导致<Event eid="e4"><Object oid="o4">车辆</Object><Denoter type="action" did="d4">起火燃烧</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e5"><Participant sid="s5，s7">省高管四大队</Participant>、<Participant sid="s5，s6">鄂州消防支队</Participant>、<Participant sid="s5，s7">武黄路政</Participant>等部门<Denoter type="action" did="d5">闻警</Denoter></Event>
<Event eid="e6">积极进行<Denoter type="operation" did="d6">救援</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e7">迅速<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d7">恢复交通</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence><Event eid="e8"><Denoter  type="emergency" did="d8">事故</Denoter>造成</Event>
<Event eid="e9"><Participant sid="s9">3人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d9">死亡</Denoter></Event><Event eid="e10"><Participant sid="s10">多人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d10">受伤</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e11"><Time type="relTime" tid="t11">目前</Time>，<Participant sid="s11">部分伤者</Participant>被<Denoter type="movement" did="d11">送到</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l11">黄石市二医院</Location></Event>
<Event eid="e12"><Denoter type="operation" did="d12">救治</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e13"><Time type="relTime" tid="t13">昨日凌晨1时58分</Time>，驾驶员<Participant sid="s13">李某</Participant><Denoter type="operation" did="d13">驾驶</Denoter>鄂BX15XX<Object sid="s13">轿车</Object></Event>
<Event eid="e14"><Denoter type="action" did="d14">行驶</Denoter>至<Location lid="l14">武黄向57 公里处</Location></Event>时，
因<Event eid="e15"><Location lid="l15">前方</Location><Object sid="s15">道路</Object><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d15">堵塞</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e16"><Denoter type="action" did="d16">停</Denoter>在驾驶员徐某驾驶的<Location lid="l16">鄂EB36XX 重型平板半挂货车后面</Location>。</Event></Sentence>
<Sentence><Event eid="e17"><Time type="relTime" tid="t17">随后</Time>，一辆“鄂A27XX”半挂<Object sid="s17">货车</Object>从后方行车道内驶来<Denoter type="action" did="d17">撞上</Denoter>鄂BX15XX<Object oid="o17">轿车</Object></Event>，
<Event eid="e18">半挂<Object sid="s18">货车</Object><Denoter type="action" did="d18">起火燃烧</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e19">并<Denoter type="action" did="d19">引燃</Denoter><Object oid="o19">其他车辆</Object></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e20"><Denoter type="operation" did="d20">接警</Denoter></Event>后，
<Event eid="e21"><Participant sid="s21">省高管支队四大队民警</Participant>在10 分钟内<Denoter type="movement" did="d21">赶到</Denoter><Location type="destination" lid="l21">现场</Location></Event>。</Sentence>
<Sentence>由于<Event eid="e22"><Object sid="s22">火势</Object>逐渐<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d22">扩大</Denoter></Event>，已造成<Event eid="e23"><Object oid="o23">交通</Object><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d23">堵塞</Denoter></Event>，并对其他车辆造成威胁，
<Event eid="e24">赶到现场的<Participant sid="s24">民警</Participant><Time type="relTime" tid="t24">立即</Time><Denoter type="operation" did="d24">分成</Denoter>几个小组</Event>，
<Event eid="e25"><Participant sid="s25，s26">一个组</Participant>负责<Denoter type="operation" did="d25">划定</Denoter><Object oid="o25">警戒区域</Object></Event>，
<Event eid="e26"><Denoter type="operation" did="d26">组织</Denoter><Participant sid="s26，s27">人员</Participant></Event><Event eid="e27"><Denoter type="operation" did="d27">灭火</Denoter></Event>；
<Event eid="e28"><Participant sid="s28">一个组</Participant>负责在<Location lid="l28">堵塞的车辆后方</Location>进行<Denoter type="operation" did="d28">警戒</Denoter></Event>；
<Event eid="e29"><Participant sid="s29，s30">一个组</Participant>负责在<Location lid="l29">泽林站口</Location><Denoter type="operation" did="d29">分流</Denoter>武汉至黄石的<Object oid="o29">车辆</Object></Event>，
<Event eid="e30">同时迅速向<Participant sid="s30">鄂州市消防支队</Participant>请求<Denoter type="operation" did="d30">支援</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
